The paper discusses a new programming model for OLTP systems, which is a subfield of database systems (cs.DB). The proposed model involves partitioning the application logic units, which relates to distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also mentions the ability to reason about program performance, which is a topic in programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE).
